parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number. Pages start from page 1. Default value: **1**.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Default value: **10**.

parameters.name: ResourceGroupId
parameters.description:
The ID of the resource group to which the Anti-DDoS Origin instance belongs in Resource Management. This parameter is empty by default, which indicates that the instance belongs to the default resource group.

For more information about resource groups, see [Create a resource group](~~94485~~).
